pare:</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-163_">NHS Trusts</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-165_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-166_">Run by a Board of Directors (Exec &amp; Non-Exec) appointed via NHS England
